Älvdalen.title: Älvdalen
Älvdalen.byline: Älvdalen is a municipality in north-western Dalarna, at the border of Härjedalen and Norway.

Älvkarleby.title: Älvkarleby
Älvkarleby.byline: Älvkarleby is a town and municipality at the northern edge of Uppsala County, where Dalälven reaches the Baltic Sea, between Tierp and Gävle.
